== Ruby jQuery chat

This app is based on Anant Garg's php jquery chat (http://anantgarg.com/2009/05/13/gmail-facebook-style-jquery-chat/)

== Getting Started

1. Download the app
2. Config your database (config/database.yml)
3. Create the db and the schema
4. Start the server
5. Open two o three different web browsers
6. In the first open: http://localhost:3000/chat/samplea
   In the second open: http://localhost:3000/chat/sampleb
   In the third open: http://localhost:3000/chat/samplec
7. Begin to chat
